               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420613-name-989" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-989" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-989" type="surname" value="HARE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-989" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS HARE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable A</hi> 103.) I was on duty at Westmin<lb></lb>ster on the morning of the 7th of June—I saw the prosecutor listening to the band, and the prisoner close behind him—I watched, and as the sol<lb></lb>diers were coming out of the archway I saw the prisoner get closer to the prosecutor, and turn from him with this handkerchief in his right hand—I took him—he dropped the handkerchief—the prosecutor turned round, and owned it—the prisoner said he had not had it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420613-name-990" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-990" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-990" type="surname" value="HEMERY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-990" type="given" value="PHILIP"></interp>PHILIP HEMERY</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in St. James's-place, Hampstead-road. I was in the Colour-yard, at St. James's, about eleven o'clock in the morn<lb></lb>ing of the 7th of June—I put my hand to my pocket, for my handkerchief, and missed it—I turned, and saw it in the policeman's hand—he was in the act of seizing the prisoner—it was safe in my pocket two or three mi<lb></lb>nutes before—this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoners Defence.</hi> I was listening to the band, and as I was coming out the policeman seized me, and said, "What do you mean by picking that man's pocket?" there were two or three men between me and the</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184206130178"></xptr>
               <p>prosecutor; he said he saw it in my hand, and the prosecutor said he did not.</p>
